cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting PUSCH antenna ports to an invalid value of 99 will cause physical layer configuration errors and prevent proper uplink transmission setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PUSCH 天線埠設定為無效值 99 會導致實體層配置錯誤，並阻止正確的上行鏈路傳輸設定。
